narration.text: The Quantum Simulation Machine is what your will be operating from this interface. We built this machine based on observations in nature. But not on the scale you are fammiliar with . . Not even in the atomic scale. Rather in the sub-atomic - or quantum scale. . In this machine the laws of physics are not the same! The moment the two particles enter this machine they have already collided in the real world. But in this machine we can observe and control the transformations they undergo, until they eventually produce the products of the collision. With this introduction you are now ready to start the journey of understanding the fundamental particle collisions.
